-- Dashboard logic comparison
-- 1. Total Wisdom contacts (comment LIKE %wisdom% OR %31daywisdomchallenge%)
WITH wisdom_contacts AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT contact_id
  FROM analytics_events
  WHERE comment ILIKE '%wisdom%' OR comment ILIKE '%31daywisdomchallenge%'
),
-- 2. Paid Ads contacts (comment LIKE %31daywisdom.com%)
paid_ads_contacts AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT contact_id
  FROM analytics_events
  WHERE comment ILIKE '%31daywisdom.com%' OR value ILIKE '%31daywisdom.com%'
),
-- 3. Your query (comment LIKE %31daywisdomchallenge.com%)
your_query_contacts AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT contact_id
  FROM analytics_events
  WHERE comment ILIKE '%31daywisdomchallenge.com%'
)
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM wisdom_contacts) AS total_wisdom,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM paid_ads_contacts) AS paid_ads,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM wisdom_contacts WHERE contact_id NOT IN (SELECT contact_id FROM paid_ads_contacts)) AS organic_dashboard,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM your_query_contacts) AS your_query_organic;
